{"tid":1647060,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］［集思廣益］台灣佬幫我地分析下一步應該點做 又整左反送中嘅感人片段 唔係唔支持下佢啊？","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:17:25.000Z","uid":231478,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65ac9d49008d685375890f9f8fd711cc1e7bea29","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"依嗰台灣佬一開始就係度講 係度分析 仲整左嗰反送中感人片段 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位手足 如果覺得攰嘅 可以睇下佢嗰頻道d片 睇翻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地依4嗰月嘅抗爭經過咁！比d動力一齊撐落去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依條片係佢近排出嘅 分析而家中共想做d咩 而家嘅局勢對中共係點嚴峻 同時仲比左d建議我地香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講明先 唔係話一定要跟佢嘅建議去做 純綷我個人覺得佢分析都幾有道理 不過無論點都好 依場仗到而家都未輸嘅原因係因為大台同軍師都係大家 遇到咩問題都係大家一齊去解決 和理非同勇武都不割 香港人要反抗！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x9PyCncL698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx9PyCncL698&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=6957705f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x9PyCncL698</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後大家係度討論下 唔by佢建議嘅 可以係度留言我地應該下一步點做（因為佢分析都分析得幾全面 簡單d講係比問題我地去拆 所以我想大家一齊係度集思廣益）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5663395b2cb9c4159afdf2e4f97e6685d288cdc","tid":1647060,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再做free rider，Twitter reddit 文宣 連儂 全民口罩，你地大把野可以做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a9e55bf38bfa41bd7e35b71311a005c07455035","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"afdddbb97368c8ff9fb2f8b86004aa1c11899d07","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"依場仗 香港人嗰個都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5072688e3264263b0597d08982e1e92537ecfa6c","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"37644a5146f59c15d62e29c0d647bf65f0ff396b","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"543962cc8b162dde27eb8778545ad3aa8415c80d","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！！！"},{"pid":"7499304806999a44e80086afd761991a57853ef0","tid":1647060,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"大家一齊集思廣益啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccd91ca1d32f516710237a3f9cc08ef00847a1f","tid":1647060